00:03:56.150 --> 00:04:02.570
Okay, the BGN's mission was to
resolve geographic name conflicts

00:04:02.570 --> 00:04:05.820
and promote the uniform
use of geographic names

00:04:05.820 --> 00:04:08.910
for the federal government.

00:04:08.910 --> 00:04:11.770
Theodore Roosevelt
expanded the Board's mission

00:04:11.770 --> 00:04:16.450
to include all issues related
to geographic names in 1906.

00:04:16.450 --> 00:04:19.390
And this was also done
by executive order.

00:04:20.790 --> 00:04:25.370
Congress re-established the
Board in its current form

00:04:25.370 --> 00:04:29.330
in 1947 under public law.

00:04:29.330 --> 00:04:35.560
So today the Board works conjointly
with the Secretary of the Interior

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:40.940
who has ultimate authority over
the Board's decisions and policies.

00:04:42.380 --> 00:04:44.690
Throughout the years the challenge

00:04:44.690 --> 00:04:48.200
of geographic names has
remained a constant.

00:04:49.390 --> 00:04:55.060
As much as in 1890, they
are still ambiguous,

00:04:55.060 --> 00:05:00.570
contested, complex, and changing.

00:05:00.570 --> 00:05:02.250
Yes, constantly changing.

00:05:02.250 --> 00:05:03.550
It's hard to believe.

00:05:03.550 --> 00:05:05.400
For many it seems like
a glacial pace,

00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:09.350
but there's a lot of
activity going on.

00:05:09.350 --> 00:05:15.160 position:56%
In the BGN's first year of operation
it processed around 2000 names,

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:19.510
which was pretty remarkable for
the time, and a lot of work.

00:05:21.060 --> 00:05:26.000
In fiscal year 2014, the
last complete fiscal year,

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:33.190
the BGN added over 700,000 new
names and made close to a million

00:05:33.190 --> 00:05:38.190
and a half edits in
the existing names.

00:05:38.190 --> 00:05:40.960
This was not an atypical year.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:48.440
So it is a great pleasure to
have you here today to reflect

00:05:48.440 --> 00:05:54.410
on our geographic names, to
celebrate 125 years of history

00:05:54.410 --> 00:05:58.240
