into consideration.

00:14:16.510 --> 00:14:20.500
And then, of course, there's one
more, and that reflects the policy

00:14:20.500 --> 00:14:23.610
that had been in place since
the 1960s for the Board

00:14:23.610 --> 00:14:27.510
to help protect it from any
apparent politicization,

00:14:27.510 --> 00:14:35.130 position:56%
which was to avoid action when there
was pending congressional action.

00:14:35.130 --> 00:14:39.800
And -- which was very sensible,
but it might have been used a bit

00:14:39.800 --> 00:14:44.570 position:56%
by the Ohio delegation which made
sure there was pending congressional

00:14:44.570 --> 00:14:51.680
