00:17:33.080 --> 00:17:36.890
The usefulness of standardizing
geographic names is well-proven,

00:17:36.890 --> 00:17:38.980
even if it's often
taken for granted.

00:17:38.980 --> 00:17:42.470 position:56%
The United Nations actively supports
international standardization

00:17:42.470 --> 00:17:45.790
of geographic names by
encouraging strong programs

00:17:45.790 --> 00:17:47.640
of national standardization.

00:17:47.640 --> 00:17:50.150
Indeed, more than 50
