01:03:43.460 --> 01:03:47.720
This starts back in
1959 with a resolution

01:03:47.720 --> 01:03:50.370
of the Economic and Social Council.

01:03:50.370 --> 01:03:54.630
And the first meetings
were held in the 1960s.

01:03:54.630 --> 01:03:56.840
