been 10 conferences

01:03:56.840 --> 01:03:59.620
and 28 meetings of
the Group of Experts.

01:03:59.620 --> 01:04:04.430
And it all started with the
idea of improving communication

01:04:04.430 --> 01:04:07.960
with geographic names, particularly
for the U.N. cartography,

01:04:07.960 --> 01:04:13.540
and the idea being of standardizing
spelling and also applications.

01:04:13.540 --> 01:04:15.840
