first conference has lived on

01:04:32.960 --> 01:04:36.760
and still is one of our very
valuable resolutions making

01:04:36.760 --> 01:04:39.010
these statements.

01:04:39.010 --> 01:04:43.510
So if the basis is
national standardization,

01:04:43.510 --> 01:04:47.050
then the cornerstone is
the names authorities.

01:04:47.050 --> 01:04:50.890
