01:04:52.190 --> 01:04:55.930
This depends upon the type
of government you have,

01:04:55.930 --> 01:04:58.600
the size of the country,
the population distribution,

01:04:58.600 --> 01:05:01.690
the number of languages,
and so on, and so on.

01:05:01.690 --> 01:05:04.300
We do have some sort of
basic thoughts on this.

01:05:04.300 --> 01:05:09.190 position:56%
