03:21:16.100 --> 03:21:17.400
Okay, so how do you get --

03:21:17.400 --> 03:21:19.140
you increase the participation
of your volunteers?

03:21:19.140 --> 03:21:21.250
Well, you provide them with
recognition and reward.

03:21:21.250 --> 03:21:23.400
It seems pretty simple, but
it's pretty straightforward.

03:21:23.400 --> 03:21:24.700
I got a pen.

03:21:24.700 --> 03:21:28.520
You know, it makes me feel
good and I appreciate that.

03:21:28.520 --> 03:21:29.820
Okay, you make it easy.

03:21:29.820 --> 03:21:31.800
And this is probably one of
the most important things,

03:21:31.800 --> 03:21:34.050
and it's been pointed out
with people I've talked

03:21:34.050 --> 03:21:39.240
to multiple times, is you make
their work, you minimize the amount

03:21:39.240 --> 03:21:42.280
of input that they have to do.

03:21:42.280 --> 03:21:45.820 position:56%
Minimize their work, make it simple.

03:21:45.820 --> 03:21:47.840
Give them tools to work with.

03:21:47.840 --> 03:21:53.510
Provide them training and with
user guides, WebEx is great.

03:21:53.510 --> 03:21:56.860
You know a lot of the travel that
we've done has been cut down simply

03:21:56.860 --> 03:22:00.380
because you can stay in your own
office and talk with a group of 20,

