You need to make it simple.

03:23:38.960 --> 03:23:40.450
I've already talked about that.

03:23:40.450 --> 03:23:42.440
You need to develop data
checking procedures,

03:23:42.440 --> 03:23:43.790
and I'll get back to that.

03:23:43.790 --> 03:23:46.530
Whether it's sampling, you can go
and sample the data that's coming

03:23:46.530 --> 03:23:49.250
in by volunteers, or
there's automation processes

03:23:49.250 --> 03:23:50.750
that are being developed.

03:23:50.750 --> 03:23:54.650
And track and evaluate the
data input by provider.

03:23:54.650 --> 03:24:03.240 position:56%
Which leads us right into creating a
trusted data source, which the core

03:24:03.240 --> 03:24:07.160
