03:53:10.800 --> 03:53:14.290
He stressed that in regard to the
former class, the primary principle

03:53:14.290 --> 03:53:16.620
which controls the
decisions of the board is

03:53:16.620 --> 03:53:20.260
that commonly local usage
[inaudible] prevail.

03:53:20.260 --> 03:53:25.150
Although Puerto Rico had been
