1899 article attests,

03:53:35.220 --> 03:53:38.480
continued to promote
the use of the variant

03:53:38.480 --> 03:53:43.360
if not archaic form of
the name, Porto Rico.

03:53:43.360 --> 03:53:47.250
Nine months after this
publication, his --

03:53:47.250 --> 03:53:49.870
of his article, Hill continued
the debate over the name

03:53:49.870 --> 03:53:52.650
of the newly seated territory
